            <td bgcolor="#4866a1"><font face="verdana" color=#D7D3DE size=2>I agree with Robin... there are many links in the Rescue Section of this website, where you can find many organizations which have dogs looking for homes. &nbsp;Children and puppies can get along, as long as you teach them both respect for one another. <br> <br>Maybe get some books, too. There are a lot of good training guides out now. <br> <br><img src="http://www.xmission.com/~lucyblue/ikonboard/emoticons/smile.gif" border="0">
