        <tr>
            <td bgcolor="#4866a1"><font face="verdana" color=#D7D3DE size=2>Hello, my wife and I would like help on purchasing a puppy for our children for this Christmas. &nbsp;I know that Christmas isn't the best time for puppies, but we have talked and feel that our boy (11 years old) would really benefit, since he has been asking for one for two years now. &nbsp;We are looking for a mild manner medium to small dog, with short hair. &nbsp;We are thinking about a Beagle, but are unsure where to start. &nbsp;Any help would be appreciated.
